        <div class="card">
          <h2>Quick Summary</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Overall stability: <b>Needs Attention</b> (0/100).</li>
            <li>Fit risk: <b>High</b>; rider level: <b>Beginner</b> (17/100).</li>
            <li>Warnings: Noticeable saddle drift detected (forward/back or sliding).; Shoulder/hip alignment variance detected (uneven rider balance).; Higher vertical bounce detected in saddle midpoint.</li>
            <li>Video quality: 17.4% tracking across 212 frames.</li>
            <li>Next step: Review girth placement/tension and pad grip. Round-barrel horses may need stability solutions.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card grid">
          <div>
            <h3 class="section-title">Flags</h3>
            <ul><li>Noticeable saddle drift detected (forward/back or sliding).</li><li>Shoulder/hip alignment variance detected (uneven rider balance).</li><li>Higher vertical bounce detected in saddle midpoint.</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="section-title">Recommendations</h3>
            <ul><li>Review girth placement/tension and pad grip. Round-barrel horses may need stability solutions.</li><li>Coach note: work on even weight in both stirrups; ride straight lines and check saddle straightness.</li><li>Focus on core engagement and softer landing in the saddle to reduce bounce.</li><li>Cadence not detected (short video or limited motion); film 30-60s with consistent trot/canter for rhythm.</li><li>Rider level estimate: Beginner (17/100). Focus on steady shoulders/hips and straight lines.</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>

